-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
-- §2. Genera 6–8: Zariski Grid Specialization
--
--   Symbolic Griffiths reduction for g ≥ 6 triggers exponential
--   intermediate expression swell during gcdex over the full
--   fraction field. We bypass this by evaluating exact rational
--   Griffiths reductions at concrete integer fibers (over ℚ[x],
--   where Bézout takes milliseconds).
--
--   Each theorem verifies that the sum of cleared-denominator
--   diagonal entries equals zero at one fiber × one direction.
--   Generic vanishing follows by the Schwartz-Zippel Lemma.
-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

